<plot>A story of Hobo and Rome, two men who live on the fringes of society, but hold on to life through their dreams and friendship. An older man, Rome, laments that he stopped dreaming. He feels that maybe death is approaching. The industrious and quick-witted Hobo sets out to bring one of his friend's past dreams to life by taking advantage of the wound-up society around him.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?242242</url></doc>
